Package: jheem.core
Type: Package
Title: Core Data Structures and Utilities for JHEEM
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-11-20
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anthony", "Fojo", email = "anthony.fojo@jhmi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Foundation package for JHEEM (Johns Hopkins HIV Epidemic Modeling).
    Provides core data structures (ontologies for multi-dimensional data),
    helper functions for array/dimension manipulation, age/year utilities,
    and version management. This package has zero dependencies on other
    jheem packages and can be used standalone.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.10),
    reshape2,
    locations,
    stringr,
    ungroup
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
